{"tid":1784550,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"關於黑警濫捕問題，希望大家集思廣益","createTime":"2019-12-15T17:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T09:31:19.000Z","uid":253688,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fcb2164b6df9187708773012208696f8d4aa3b5a","tid":1784550,"uid":253688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:39:36.000Z","msg":"依家黑警拉你後好多時冇咩證據，就照拉你上庭等你嘥錢嘥時間！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔可以踢保又唔出得黎，最重要咁岩預到紅底官分分鐘句入埋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇咩方法可以減少鳩我拉上庭，或者可以有證明班狗係冇足夠證據就拉人上庭，令到之前俾人鳩告既人可以撤銷控罪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc229af0c5e08a13857ff90c96c1946bb0f426d","tid":1784550,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:42:40.000Z","msg":"唔識<br />\n幫推<br />\n最近好似多左一兩架狗車停住宅區附近成隊十幾個恐怖分子咁，唔知係咪準備鳩拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17eb9fb8180c4824e424639bfdf3a674ad3c8730","tid":1784550,"uid":253688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:50:09.000Z","msg":"自推一下，希望有方法幫到被捕手足！<br />\n如果眾籌俾班律師告黑警或者叫班律師聯署投訴黑警有冇得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最重要有方法引起社會或者國際關注依件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37104a34d03979851e9292e28682f72b1ade1029","tid":1784550,"uid":184366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:53:02.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9573e0e49845f358811cfd7e8d341ec4664eb5","tid":1784550,"uid":253688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:02:25.000Z","msg":"推，暖氣軍師入黎俾d意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49864da6dda14bb0e14a158a5ad0f0927903ca54","tid":1784550,"uid":253688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T23:03:1